STATE EX REL. CLEMONS
v.
KASICH 2018-1188 Supreme Court of Ohio. November 7, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

*19O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell, Kennedy, French, Fischer, DeWine, and DeGenaro, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Mandamus. On respondent's motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed. Relator's "motion to expedite and emergency relief" denied.
